aces; background-color: rgba(175, 184, 193, 0.2); border-radius: 6px; margin: 0px; padding: 0.2em 0.4em; scrollbar-color: rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.5) rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.1) !important;\">Ctrl+Shift+P</code>&nbsp;and type&nbsp;<code style=\"--tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-pan-x: ; --tw-pan-y: ; --tw-pinch-zoom: ; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-gradient-from-position: ; --tw-gradient-via-position: ; --tw-gradient-to-position: ; --tw-ordinal: ; --tw-slashed-zero: ; --tw-numeric-figure: ; --tw-numeric-spacing: ; --tw-numeric-fraction: ; --tw-ring-inset: ; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgb(59 130 246 / 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; --tw-blur: ; --tw-brightness: ; --tw-contrast: ; --tw-grayscale: ; --tw-hue-rotate: ; --tw-invert: ; --tw-saturate: ; --tw-sepia: ; --tw-drop-shadow: ; --tw-backdrop-blur: ; --tw-backdrop-brightness: ; --tw-backdrop-contrast: ; --tw-backdrop-grayscale: ; --tw-backdrop-hue-rotate: ; --tw-backdrop-invert: ; --tw-backdrop-opacity: ; --tw-backdrop-saturate: ; --tw-backdrop-sepia: ; --tw-contain-size: ; --tw-contain-layout: ; --tw-contain-paint: ; --tw-contain-style: ; box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(229, 231, 235); font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-size: 13.6px; white-space-collapse: break-spaces; background-color: rgba(175, 184, 193, 0.2); border-radius: 6px; margin: 0px; padding: 0.2em 0.4em; scrollbar-color: rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.5) rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.1) !important;\">Deno: Initialize Workspace Configuration</code>. Select this option to configure Deno for your workspace.</p>"}}, "style": {"font-family": "\"Lato\", sans-serif"}, "pageId": "9461c09e-a437-49b0-9a51-d040d7edf431", "childrens": [], "children_ids": [], "application_id": "838669d8-92d2-4342-baba-5f32a40eef42"}, {"name": "text_label_3184_rnst", "type": "text_label", "uuid": "2011342c-5804-4cba-ba60-909dcf6c938e", "input": {"value": {"type": "value", "value": "Button"}}, "style": {"fontSize": "30px", "margin-top": "10px", "font-family": "\"Mulish\", sans-serif"}, "pageId": "9461c09e-a437-49b0-9a51-d040d7edf431", "childrens": [], "children_ids": [], "application_id": "838669d8-92d2-4342-baba-5f32a40eef42"}, {"name": "rich-text_700", "type": "rich_text", "uuid": "f334cdb8-64a8-4067-8d11-153d297381a8", "input": {"value": {"type": "string", "value": "<h2 class=\"anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7\" id=\"when-to-use\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(28, 30, 33); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; line-height: 1.25; margin: 40px 0px 20px; font-size: 32px; scroll-margin-top: 68px; --ifm-h2-font-size: 2rem;\">When To Use<a href=\"https://hybridui.github.io/docs/docs/components/buttons#when-to-use\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to When To Use\" title=\"Direct link to When To Use\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.2s; color: rgb(46, 133, 85); text-decoration-line: none; text-decoration-style: solid; text-decoration-color: rgb(46, 133, 85); opacity: 0; padding-left: 0.5rem; user-select: none;\">ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Â ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã¢â€žÂ¢ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã‚Â ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¾Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã‚Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Â ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã¢â€žÂ¢ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã‚Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¬ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã‚Â¦ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã‚Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¬ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Â ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã¢â€žÂ¢ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¬ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Â¦Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¬ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã‚Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¹</a></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(28, 30, 33); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px;\">Buttons in Hybrid Design are used to perform one or more operations. When clicked, a button triggers the corresponding business logic. In Hybrid Design, we offer five types of buttons:</p><ul class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding-left: 32px; color: rgb(28, 30, 33); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Primary button: This button indicates the main action and there should only be one primary button in each section.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 4px;\">Default button: This button represents a series of actions without priority.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 4px;\">Dashed button: This button is commonly used for adding an action.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 4px;\">Text button: This button is used for the most secondary action.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 4px;\">Link button: This button is used for external links.</li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(28, 30, 33); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px;\">Additionally, we have four other properties that can be applied to any type of button:</p><ul class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding-left: 32px; color: rgb(28, 30, 33); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: middle; background-color: rgb(246, 247, 248); border: 0.1rem solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); border-radius: 6.4px; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.2px; padding: 1.6px;\">danger</code>: This property is used for actions that involve risk, such as deletion or authorization.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 4px;\"><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: middle; background-color: rgb(246, 247, 248); border: 0.1rem solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); border-radius: 6.4px; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.2px; padding: 1.6px;\">disabled</code>: This property indicates when actions are not available.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 4px;\"><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: middle; background-color: rgb(246, 247, 248); border: 0.1rem solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); border-radius: 6.4px; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.2px; padding: 1.6px;\">loading</code>: This property adds a loading spinner to the button, preventing multiple submits.</li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(28, 30, 33); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px;\">In HybridUI, the available button types are primary, default, dashed, text, and link.</p>"}}, "pageId": "9461c09e-a437-49b0-9a51-d040d7edf431", "childrens": [], "children_ids": [], "application_id": "838669d8-92d2-4342-baba-5f32a40eef42"}, {"name": "button-demo-block", "type": "container", "uuid": "13ad228c-d0c6-4362-b072-87de7c43ff26", "pageId": "9461c09e-a437-49b0-9a51-d040d7edf431", "childrens": [{"name": "button_input_1901_r5tx", "type": "button_input", "uuid": "d99fdc90-d1ea-44bd-b578-159469287e4a", "input": {"label": {"type": "value", "value": "Primary button"}}, "style": {"type": "primary"}, "pageId": "9461c09e-a437-49b0-9a51-d040d7edf431", "childrens": [], "children_ids": [], "application_id": "838669d8-92d2-4342-baba-5f32a40eef42"}, {"name": "button_input_1901", "type": "button_input", "uuid": "6c520d54-b52d-4175-9ee9-f642d77255b1", "input": {"label": {"type": "value", "value": "Secondary button"}}, "style": {"type": "secondary", "margin-left": "10px"}, "pageId": "9461c09e-a437-49b0-9a51-d040d7edf431", "childrens": [], "children_ids": [], "application_id": "838669d8-92d2-4342-baba-5f32a40eef42"}, {"name": "button_input_1901_7chd", "type": "button_input", "uuid": "b9c41082-3aa6-429f-bb01-b2152ac4d01f", "input": {"label": {"type": "value", "value": "Danger button"}}, "style": {"type": "danger", "margin-left": "10px"}, "pageId": "9461c09e-a437-49b0-9a51-d040d7edf431", "childrens": [], "children_ids": [], "application_id": "838669d8-92d2-4342-baba-5f32a40eef42"}, {"name": "button_input_1901_ueky", "type": "button_input", "uuid": "02b35fee-5c1c-4941-8934-c0d7b059c256", "input": {"label": {"type": "value", "value": "Ghost button"}}, "style": {"type": "ghost", "margin-left": "10px"}, "pageId": "9461c09e-a437-49b0-9a51-d040d7edf431", "childrens": [], "children_ids": [], "application_id": "838669d8-92d2-4342-baba-5f32a40eef42"}, {"name": "button_input_1901_qtpb", "type": "button_input", "uuid": "97dfd226-0c00-4452-bd7b-cfd26bd10a20", "input": {"label": {"type": "value", "value": "Default button"}}, "style": {"type": "default", "margin-left": "10px"}, "pageId": "9461c09e-a437-49b0-9a51-d040d7edf431", "childrens": [], "children_ids": [], "application_id": "838669d8-92d2-4342-baba-5f32a40eef42"}], "children_ids": ["d99fdc90-d1ea-44bd-b578-159469287e4a", "6c520d54-b52d-4175-9ee9-f642d77255b1", "b9c41082-3aa6-429f-bb01-b2152ac4d01f", "02b35fee-5c1c-4941-8934-c0d7b059c256", "97dfd226-0c00-4452-bd7b-cfd26bd10a20"], "application_id": "838669d8-92d2-4342-baba-5f32a40eef42"}], "breakpoints": {"430px": {"input": {"layout": {"type": "string", "value": "default"}}, "style": {"width": "auto", "padding-left": "10px", "padding-right": "10px"}}}, "children_ids": ["ce54932e-c078-4eab-98c9-fb2d78dd98aa", "e1bfaeed-114a-48b7-9c95-b9ae0c41b0cd", "13ad228c-d0c6-4362-b072-87de7c43ff26"], "application_id": "838669d8-92d2-4342-baba-5f32a40eef42"}', '7a44cfff-24d1-4eec-8974-c6384303f1ba', 'ee133314-0014-4e40-b067-9682331b1aa4', '838669d8-92d2-4342-baba-5f32a40eef42') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
